race.description: Magic Millions Country Cup Qualifier Handicap
race.comment: CHERRY ROSE (2) returned in fine fashion with a strong win at Rockhampton before maybe suffering from the dreaded second-up syndrome last time out. Ready to peak now third run back and a return to form is expected. OBLIGATED (4) resumes here but has a handy record first-up with a win and a second from three fresh attempts. Makes plenty of appeal. NORTHERN PRIDE (1) is yet to miss a drum in four starts over this course and distance and rarely puts in a poor one. Shapes as one of the leading contenders. TAMBO'S JUSTICE (7) has won six from nine overall here on his home circuit and shouldn't be underestimated. TYCOON BEAU (6) next best despite the sticky alley.
